<topic id="wh-responsive-output">
  <title><?oxy_comment_start author="bogdan" timestamp="20160414T094805+0300" comment="Do not forget about the new parameters, specific to WH Responsive only."?>WebHelp
    Responsive Output<?oxy_comment_end?></title>
  <body>
    <p>To publish a DITA map as a WebHelp Responsive system:<ol>
        <li>Click <uicontrol><image href="../img/TransformConfig16.png"/>Configure Transformation
            Scenarios</uicontrol>.</li>
        <li><?oxy_comment_start author="bogdan" timestamp="20160407T100922+0300" comment="Ask BogdanC about the feedback part"?>Select
          the <uicontrol>DITA Map WebHelp Responsive</uicontrol> scenario from the <uicontrol>DITA
            Map</uicontrol> section.</li>
        <li>In the <uicontrol>Templates</uicontrol> tab, select a skin of the appropriate template
          and click <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>.</li>
        <li>Click <uicontrol>Apply associated</uicontrol>.<?oxy_comment_end?><p>When the
              <uicontrol>DITA Map WebHelp Responsive</uicontrol> transformation is complete, the
            output is automatically opened in your default browser.</p></li>
      </ol></p>
